                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240715-71-victim663 t18240715-71-viclabel376"></join>, and live in Piccadilly. On the 31st of May the prisoner was brought to my house by Dorrington, and a piece of printed cotton with him - I could not swear to it, as I had not missed any of that description.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18240715-71-person665">
                  FREDERICK 
                  DORRINGTON
               <interp inst="t18240715-71-person665" type="surname" value="DORRINGTON"></interp>
